/>\n到睇到張照又會覺得唔係好醜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:50:23.000Z","msg":"點睇都正常人水平啦 個標題好嘩眾取寵"},{"pid":"58691233bcc6e2a994f0bb5b43c101250db1a484","tid":664432,"uid":92734,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"1232ffc2b098ab7c51ce54a032eda947183004bb","tid":664432,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:33:32.000Z","msg":"每個父母都希望自己的女兒能夠嫁個好人家，近期中國大陸一名女子因為外貌不佳，一直找不到結婚對象，女子的父母霸氣開出 1618 萬人民幣（折合約2034萬港元）的嫁妝，讓女兒順利找到一位單眼皮帥哥，引發熱烈討論。網友則留言「看到新娘後釋懷了」。<br />\n<br />\n中國大陸近期在微博瘋傳 2 張照片，一張是新娘嫁妝的清單，另外一張則是新娘父母和新人的合照，而讓所有人眼睛一亮的是新娘的嫁妝，因為總價值 1618 人民幣，包含 888 萬的「龍爐香醍漫步」別墅，還有一棟 398 萬人民幣的公寓等等，難怪在新人與新娘父母合照時，新郎笑得特別開心。<br />\n<br />\n網友看了清單後都對這嫁妝表示羨慕「這嫁妝超狂」，但也有網友歪樓「新郎的媽媽好美」、「這種結婚最不安全的夫妻，離婚指數 5 顆星」、「女的要是不化妝，可能要醜到天際去」。並有人酸「看到新娘釋懷了，難怪嫁妝這麼多」，甚至留言「都出得起 1618 萬，幹嘛不去整形」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ppbFqI3qxYJfLCmjCoUiUQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/c1ad67712e5da553ac9142f529e688fb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FppbFqI3qxYJfLCmjCoUiUQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fc1ad67712e5da553ac9142f529e688fb&h=7ada0844&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xFh7FMnFM4EuTiLr8UEVWA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9ODA5/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/503dcfa99a80518b6c59f07c96606f70\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FxFh7FMnFM4EuTiLr8UEVWA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9ODA5%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F503dcfa99a80518b6c59f07c96606f70&h=d0ce84c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A5%B3%E6%96%B9%E8%B1%AA%E9%80%812034%E8%90%AC%E5%AB%81%E5%A6%9D%E3%80%80%E7%B6%B